c: 20
v: 88
t: "Ni ŵakopochesye (Saamiriyyu kuumila pamoto pala kasanamu ka) kang’ombe kakaliji kana chiŵiliŵili chakwanila, kakatendaga mpela kakutwamula. Basi ŵanganyao ni ŵatite: “Aju ni nnungu jwenu soni ni nnungu jwa Musa, gamba kuti (Musa) juliŵalile (niligongo lyakwe jujile kunsosa kwitumbi).”"